就是你了，你是凯撒
You are him. You're Caesar.

57
00:09:47,390 --> 00:09:49,170
我们找你已有段时间了
We've been searching for you for so long.

58
00:09:50,030 --> 00:09:53,570
我们听闻你拥有一个秘密的指挥基地，但我们从来没有找到它
We heard you had a hidden command base, but we could never find it.

59
00:09:53,970 --> 00:09:56,410
我们中某些人认为你可能已经死亡
Some of us were starting to think that you might be dead,

60
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:58,690
但麦卡洛上校说 你就藏在这里某处
but Colonel McCullough said you were out here somewhere.

61
00:09:58,690 --> 00:10:00,900
- 你这样干会被杀的！     - 停吧！
- You had been kill so way!     - Stop it!

62
00:10:00,900 --> 00:10:04,340
- 什么？     - 牠们是畜牲，会把我们吞掉
- What?     - They're animals. He's gonna swallow us.

63
00:10:11,420 --> 00:10:16,020
我没有挑起这场战争
I did not start this war.

64
00:10:17,160 --> 00:10:19,850
引发战争的猿猴…已死了
The Ape who did... is dead.

65
00:10:21,750 --> 00:10:24,100
他的名字叫高巴
His name was Koba.

66
00:10:24,100 --> 00:10:25,800
我杀了他
I killed him.

67
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:34,240
- 现在，我只为保护猿猴们而战斗     - 是吗？
- Now, I'm fight only to protect the Apes.     - Yeah?

68
00:10:36,810 --> 00:10:40,440
那他如何？ 我们还有十个以上像他那样
What about him? We got ten more like him.

69
00:10:41,640 --> 00:10:45,980
我认识这些猿猴们，他们追随高巴
I know these Apes. They followed Koba.

70
00:10:48,090 --> 00:10:49,790
他们尝试杀了我
They tried to kill me.

71
00:10:50,570 --> 00:10:54,030
他们害怕我将会怎样对待他们
They fear what I would do to them.

72
00:10:54,060 --> 00:10:55,760
所以现在…
So now...

73
00:10:56,160 --> 00:10:57,900
他们顺从你…
They serve you...

74
00:10:58,740 --> 00:11:00,440
只是为了活命
Just to survive.

75
00:11:02,470 --> 00:11:05,300
我并不怕你！
I don't fear you!

76
00:11:09,020 --> 00:11:12,070
你定是恐惧了！
You must fear!

77
00:11:12,790 --> 00:11:17,120
你认为丛林还能保护你多久？
How long you think woods can protect you?

78
00:11:17,150 --> 00:11:19,750
人类要灭掉你
Humans destroy you.

79
