"Leave us passed the woods and the killing can stop."

90
00:12:38,960 --> 00:12:42,300
你认为他们会将讯息传递给他吗？
Do you think they will give him the message?

91
00:12:42,500 --> 00:12:45,070
他们本身就是个口讯，莫利斯
They are the message, Morris.

92
00:12:45,720 --> 00:12:48,180
他会明白到我们并非野蛮人
He will see we are not savages.

93
00:12:56,170 --> 00:12:59,720
那叛徒袭击了我！ 他逃走了！
The traitor attacked me! He got away!

94
00:13:27,330 --> 00:13:30,390
高巴仍继续缠扰着我们
Koba still haunts us.

95
00:13:33,290 --> 00:13:40,190
我看不见他会原谅人类对他作出的恶行
I did not seen that he could not forgive what humans did to him.

96
00:13:41,770 --> 00:13:45,230
