那些山脉背后有什么东西，儿子？
What is beyond those mountains, son?

112
00:16:33,250 --> 00:16:35,370
给他们看，洛基
Show them, Rocket.

113
00:16:47,870 --> 00:16:49,350
一个沙漠！
A desert!

114
00:16:49,350 --> 00:16:52,060
路途遥远
The journey is long...

115
00:16:52,490 --> 00:16:54,850
但就因为这样，人类才找不到我们
But that is why humans will not find us.

116
00:16:55,360 --> 00:16:57,830
