今晚？ 这不可能吧！
Tonight? That's impossible!

118
00:17:00,710 --> 00:17:02,300
我们还能等多久，力克？
How long can we wait, Lake?

119
00:17:02,300 --> 00:17:04,360
士兵越来越近了！
Soldiers getting closer!

120
00:17:04,360 --> 00:17:05,560
温达
Winter.

121
