Get them!

137
00:20:14,530 --> 00:20:16,760
路加，与华格道同去
Luca, go with Raketa.

138
00:21:10,030 --> 00:21:11,960
单位呼叫指挥，上校请答话
Unit calling command, Colonel.

139
00:21:22,600 --> 00:21:24,500
洛基，发生什么事？
Rocket? What happening?

140
00:21:24,500 --> 00:21:27,300
我听到他的通话！ 上校已到这里了！
I heard him talking! The Colonel is here!

141
