Loudly I, target acquired. Repeat, King Kong is dead.

143
00:21:37,430 --> 00:21:40,080
走吧！ 我将由这里往上撤
Let's go. I'll get up from here.

144
00:23:46,210 --> 00:23:47,710
凯撒
Caesar

145
00:23:48,010 --> 00:23:49,850
我们找不到温达！
We can not find Winter!

146
00:23:52,550 --> 00:23:56,400
他受惊了！ 我怀疑他已背叛了我们！
He was Scared! I think he betrayed us!

147
00:24:00,450 --> 00:24:04,010
你找到了科尼利亚斯吗？
Have you found Cornelius yet?

148
00:24:05,140 --> 00:24:07,220
我们仍在找
We're still searching.

149
00:24:11,880 --> 00:24:15,230
那去找凯撒的小儿子吧
Let's go look for Caesar's little son.

150
00:24:48,830 --> 00:24:50,830
过来，科尼利亚斯
Come, Cornelius.

151
00:24:59,330 --> 00:25:01,480
你现在安全了
You are safe now.

152
00:25:19,380 --> 00:25:20,600
力克
Lake.

153
00:25:21,630 --> 00:25:23,340
你爱我的儿子
You loved my son.

154
00:25:24,080 --> 00:25:27,810
照护他的弟弟，直到我回来
Look after his brother, until I return.

155
00:25:32,700 --> 00:25:36,300
你不与我们一起到新家园去吗？
You're not coming with us to our new home?

156
00:25:36,840 --> 00:25:38,340
不了
No.

157
00:25:42,490 --> 00:25:44,190
跟力克走
Go with Lake.

158
00:25:59,940 --> 00:26:01,300
凯撒！
Caesar!

159
00:26:01,500 --> 00:26:03,520
你不跟他们一起走吗？！
You're not going after them?!

160
00:26:05,850 --> 00:26:07,570
不是他们，要找“他”
Is not them, him.

161
00:26:07,570 --> 00:26:12,340
凯撒，你是我们的领袖！
Caesar, you are our leader!

162
00:26:12,340 --> 00:26:14,470
我们没有你不能离开！
We can't leave without you!

163
00:26:15,310 --> 00:26:17,010
你必定要
You must.

164
00:26:17,870 --> 00:26:19,770
那些士兵很快便会回来
The soldiers will be back soon.

165
00:26:19,770 --> 00:26:21,960
父亲！
Father!

166
00:26:23,570 --> 00:26:27,210
当我找到他后，士兵们将会追捕我
When I find him, the soldiers will come after me.

167
00:26:28,690 --> 00:26:31,670
让我给你们一个好机会，逃出丛林
Let me give you the best chance to get out of the woods.

168
00:26:35,060 --> 00:26:37,210
他要往那里去？！
Where is he going?!

169
00:26:40,930 --> 00:26:44,440
凯撒！ 凯撒！
Caesar! Caesar!

170
00:27:33,010 --> 00:27:35,800
那些军营是经常迁移的
The soldiers' camp is always moving.

171
00:27:35,800 --> 00:27:38,160
我的护卫知道军营在哪里
My guards think they know where it is

172
00:27:38,190 --> 00:27:39,700
让我引领你
Let me take you

173
00:27:39,700 --> 00:27:42,400
你需要我来当你的后援！
You need me to back you up!

174
00:27:43,400 --> 00:27:44,700
不用！
No!

175
00:27:45,930 --> 00:27:46,900
拜托
Please.

176
00:27:47,000 --> 00:27:52,660
我知道失去了儿子的滋味
I know what it's like to lose a son

177
00:27:53,890 --> 00:27:57,300
我或许没能救他回来
I may not make him back.

178
00:27:58,520 --> 00:28:01,900
所以为什么我要跟着来
That's why I'm coming

179
00:28:03,540 --> 00:28:06,370
是为了确保你能达成
To make sure you do.

180
00:28:42,960 --> 00:28:45,400
护卫认为士兵就在这里
Guards think soldiers here.

181
00:28:45,400 --> 00:28:47,960
总是有烟火吹生
Always fires burning.

182
00:29:01,290 --> 00:29:03,100
这里没有人
No one here.

183
00:29:03,960 --> 00:29:05,600
搜索这片区域
Search the area.

184
00:29:28,800 --> 00:29:30,680
我只想将这东西放下
I'll just gonna put this down.

185
00:30:05,240 --> 00:30:07,250
他独个儿在这里干什么？
What's he doing out here alone?

186
00:30:07,690 --> 00:30:09,680
