Maybe he's a deserter?

187
00:31:22,330 --> 00:31:24,030
四处搜搜
Look around

188
00:31:27,220 --> 00:31:28,920
要什么就拿走吧
Take what you can.

189
00:33:23,150 --> 00:33:24,800
她出了点问题
Something wrong with her.

190
