仁慈
Mercy.

458
01:19:10,570 --> 01:19:13,810
你是否真的明白对我们施与仁慈的真正意义？
Do you have any idea what you mercy would do to us?

459
01:19:17,880 --> 01:19:19,830
你定是比我们坚强
You're must stronger than we are.

460
01:19:21,060 --> 01:19:22,760
聪明得如此
Smart as hell.

461
01:19:23,310 --> 01:19:27,690
不论你如何说，最终你做出了中止自然规律的行为
No matter what you say. Eventually, you play suspended the law of nature.

462
01:19:28,830 --> 01:19:30,970
铁证在前，我们创造了你
The irony is, we created you.

463
01:19:30,970 --> 01:19:34,090
你试图蔑视大自然，屈服于我们的意愿之外
You tried to defy nature, bend it to our will.

464
01:19:34,100 --> 01:19:38,400
大自然为了我们如此的傲慢而惩罚了我们
And nature has been punishing us for our arrogance ever since.

465
01:19:41,640 --> 01:19:45,090
十个月前，我派出侦察队去搜索你的基地
Ten months ago, I sent out recon units to look for your base.

466
01:19:45,120 --> 01:19:48,280
我的亲儿子是侦察队中的一名士兵
My own son was a soldier with one of the units.

467
01:19:48,760 --> 01:19:51,050
有一天他突然不再说话
One day he suddenly stopped speaking.

468
01:19:51,050 --> 01:19:53,420
