He became a primitive, like an animal.

469
01:19:53,690 --> 01:19:57,180
他们与我联络，说他们认为我儿子失了心智
They contact with me, and said that they though he lost his mind,

470
01:19:58,300 --> 01:20:00,310
这场战争让他承受太多了
The war is too much for him.

471
01:20:01,490 --> 01:20:04,500
之后带领我儿子的士兵也同样不再说话了
Then the man who carried for him stopped speaking too.

472
