军医在停止说话前提出了一个理论
The medic had a theory, before he stopped speaking,

473
01:20:10,540 --> 01:20:13,160
出现了一种病毒几乎扫清了我们
that the virus that almost wiped us out,

474
01:20:13,200 --> 01:20:16,750
每个人类幸存者依然携带着病毒
The virus that every human survivor still carries,

475
01:20:17,580 --> 01:20:21,010
情况突然转变，病毒异变了！
Had suddenly changed, mutant!

476
01:20:22,970 --> 01:20:28,070
如果异变了的病毒蔓延开去，这次将永久性地摧毁人类族群
And if it is spread, it would destroy humanity for good this time.

477
01:20:29,650 --> 01:20:35,380
不是为了杀戮我们，而是为了掠夺我们人类、
Not by killing us, but by robbing us of those things that make us human.

478
01:20:35,770 --> 01:20:39,920
我们的语言、我们高阶的思维，将我们变成一头怪物！
Our speech, our higher thinking. It would turn us into beasts!

479
01:20:40,420 --> 01:20:42,760
你跟我谈仁慈吗？
You talk about mercy?

480
01:20:44,680 --> 01:20:46,380
你会怎么干？
What would you have done?

481
01:20:49,500 --> 01:20:52,180
就是这个时刻让我清省了
It was a moment of clarity for me.

482
01:20:52,390 --> 01:20:56,580
我明白到我将要牺牲我唯一的儿子
I realized that I would have to sacrifice my only son,

483
01:20:56,620 --> 01:20:59,870
来拯救人类族群
so that humanlity could be saved.

484
01:21:02,610 --> 01:21:07,860
我拿着枪在手良久
I held that gun in my hand for a long time...

485
01:21:11,160 --> 01:21:15,760
最终把枪指向我唯一的儿子
I pointed it at my only child.

486
01:21:18,350 --> 01:21:22,890
他双眼里带着信任凝望着我
He looked me with trust in his eyes.

487
01:21:24,930 --> 01:21:29,320
甚至在他原始的目光里
Even in his primitive gaze,

488
01:21:32,960 --> 01:21:35,130
我感觉到他的...
I felt his...

489
01:21:36,310 --> 01:21:38,030
爱
Love.

490
01:21:43,850 --> 01:21:45,610
我扣下枪板
I pulled the trigger.

491
01:21:47,930 --> 01:21:50,050
它净化了我
It purify me.

492
01:21:51,530 --> 01:21:53,950
这使我的目标更为明确
It made my purpose clear.

493
01:21:55,860 --> 01:21:59,950
我下达了命令去杀尽所有已受感染的人
I gave the order to kill the others infected, all of them.

494
01:22:00,110 --> 01:22:04,190
烧光他们的随身物品及会引致污染扩散的所有东西
Burn their belongings, and anything that might spread contamination.

495
01:22:04,590 --> 01:22:07,090
他们中一些人质疑我的判断
Some of the men questioned my judgement.

496
01:22:07,120 --> 01:22:10,450
我问他们能否依样葫芦地跟我干同样的事
I was asking them to do what I had done,

497
01:22:10,540 --> 01:22:15,360
牺牲他们的朋友及他们的家庭
To sacrifice their friends, their family.

498
01:22:18,270 --> 01:22:20,490
当然地，他们拒绝了！
Of course, they refused.

499
01:22:23,140 --> 01:22:24,840
因此我把他们也杀了
So I had them killed too.

500
01:22:27,030 --> 01:22:31,640
其它人带着孩子们逃往丛林去
Others with children deserted into the woods.

501
01:22:32,950 --> 01:22:36,930
当中有一位懦夫竟跑到我北方上司那里
One of those cowards fled to my superiors up north.

502
01:22:36,970 --> 01:22:41,650
他们想说服我，说这疫症是有药可治
They tried to convince me that this plague could be dealt with medically.

503
01:22:42,300 --> 01:22:48,490
之后我才真正认识到，他们根本没从过去中汲取教训
Then I realized that they had learn nothing from our past.

504
01:22:49,650 --> 01:22:52,330
你也把他们杀掉？
You killed them too?

505
