我干了什么，牧师？
What did I do, Preacher?

506
01:22:57,640 --> 01:22:59,340
你劈下了他们的脑袋，长官
You severed their head, sir.

507
01:23:00,280 --> 01:23:02,440
除了一个，我放过了他
Except for the one I spared

508
01:23:02,640 --> 01:23:05,490
好让他能回去传递一个讯息
so that he could return to delivery a message.

509
01:23:05,760 --> 01:23:08,530
如果他们想解除我的命令
If they want to relieve me of my commands

510
