Oh, no! Friend...

554
01:28:59,130 --> 01:29:00,830
不！
No!

555
01:29:01,460 --> 01:29:03,160
不！
No!

556
01:29:03,480 --> 01:29:05,240
不！ 不要！
No! Not!

557
01:29:05,280 --> 01:29:06,980
不！ 快回来，回来！
No! Come come!

558
01:29:11,450 --> 01:29:13,840
