Join me...

567
01:30:34,490 --> 01:30:36,890
如果明早他还活着
If he's still alive in the morning.

568
01:30:42,600 --> 01:30:45,330
他也要像其它猿猴一样回去工作
He goes back to work like everyone else.

569
01:30:46,290 --> 01:30:48,090
